OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy,
OL,6,Fdamp evening with outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FTurning drier through the rest of the
OL,8,Fnight with some clearer spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Blustery winds, strong at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,13,Fdry day, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,14,Fand just the slight chance of an
OL,15,Fisolated light shower in the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,18,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,19,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter periods too.
